Baabi a na wɔde nnaka a nnompe wom sisi
Ebesi saa bere yi no, na yɛwɔ nsi a emu yɛ den nanso na yenni no nokware nimdeɛ mu.
(Kenkan Adiyisɛm 12: 9, 12.)
Ma mennantew wo nokware mu na kyerɛkyerɛ me, efisɛ wone me nkwagye Nyankopɔn.
Nhwehwɛmu a wɔayɛ nnansa yi kyerɛ sɛ, sɛ wɔde kankyee mu nnuan ne nufusu bom ma mmofra a, ɛma asiane a ɛwɔ hɔ sɛ wobenya HIV ɔyare mmoawa no yɛ kɛse, na ebetumi aba sɛ nnuannuru bi wɔ nufusu no mu a ebetumi abrɛ ɔyare mmoawa no ase.
