Nnwinnade a ahuru wom di dwuma yiye, ɛnyɛ ogya a wɔde nkyerɛwde A gyina hɔ ma nko na etumi dum no, na mmom, etumi dum ogya a ɛtɔ nneɛma a ɛyɛ nsunsu mu nso (fango, mfoninnuru), nea mpɛn pii no, wɔde nkyerɛwde B na egyina hɔ ma no.
